Lu Ming Organic Tea Competition is only open to farmers of certified organic tea. The producer of this tea has obtained MOA organic certification. Besides inspections of its organic certification institution, the tea produced by participating farmers is also regularly inspected by the organizer of this competition, Lu Ming Organic Farmer Association. The competition acknowledges high quality organic tea that has great tastes.  










