Lu Ming Tang flagship store by Design Overlay, Hangzhou – China


                            May 9th, 2017 by retail design blog                                            




“Healthy Beauty by Tea” – Start-up brand created by the French Entrepreneur Marie Amiand, Lu Ming Tang extract it’s active ingredients from the highest quality organic teas of Longjing, providing safe detoxifying solutions to modern urban skins.

Overlay is proud to have been the brand partner’s to their first store in Hangzhou prestigious ShangriLa and is now working on its Shanghai boutique Flagship.

Generous & whimsical – the store is a made of a collection of memories from Marie’s quest to the healthiest Cosmetic products. From Parisian inspiration with Louis XVI furniture’s to Chinese ornaments arranged with French moldings tradition, the whole space derives from the mélange of two of the richest Cultures in the world. 
Design: Design Overlay














                            Posted in cosmetics 
                            Tags: china, cosmetics, Design Overlay, Hangzhou, Lu Ming Tang, stores 

